[2026-05-19T01:39:12.514Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_h0jsjtcat0t0_1","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Education — Screen Specification\n2\t\n3\t## 1. Screen Title\n4\t\n5\t**Education**\n6\t\n7\t---\n8\t\n9\t## 2. Purpose\n10\t\n11\tBrowse and read trusted educational articles organized by topic. This screen serves as a content discovery hub, allowing users to explore curated health information relevant to their pregnancy journey. Users can filter by topic, search articles, and bookmark content for later reference.\n12\t\n13\t**Context:** Push route from Library tab. BottomNavigationBar is hidden. Primary actions are topic filtering, search, and article navigation.\n14\t\n15\t---\n16\t\n17\t## 3. Route\n18\t\n19\t`/education`\n20\t\n21\t---\n22\t\n23\t## 4. Widget Name\n24\t\n25\t`EducationScreen`\n26\t\n27\t---\n28\t\n29\t## 5. Design Tokens\n30\t\n31\t### Colors (Light Theme — from DESIGN.md Section 2)\n32\t\n33\t| Token | Hex | Usage |\n34\t|---|---|---|\n35\t| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary brand, AppBar, topic icons (Nutrition, Maternal Care) |\n36\t| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n37\t| `blushRose` | `#F9A8D4` | Secondary accent, Mental Health topic icon |\n38\t| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Tertiary, success states, bookmark active indicator |\n39\t| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n40\t| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text |\n41\t| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, captions, timestamps |\n42\t| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | Borders, dividers |\n43\t| `softCoral` | `#EF4444` | Error states |\n44\t| `warmWhite` | `#FFFFFF` | Bottom nav background, sheets |\n45\t\n46\t### Colors (Dark Theme)\n47\t\n48\t| Token | Hex | Usage |\n49\t|---|---|---|\n50\t| `twilightBloom` | `#9F67FF` | Primary brand in dark mode |\n51\t| `duskyRose` | `#FBC4E0` | Secondary accent in dark mode |\n52\t| `nightMint` | `#34D399` | Tertiary success in dark mode |\n53\t| `deepTwilight` | `#1E1B2E` | Card backgrounds in dark mode |\n54\t| `nightSky` | `#13111C` | Scaffold background in dark mode |\n55\t| `softPearl` | `#F3F4F6` | Primary text in dark mode |\n56\t| `mutedSilver` | `#9CA3AF` | Secondary text in dark mode |\n57\t| `deepBorder` | `#2D2B3A` | Borders in dark mode |\n58\t\n59\t### Typography (Nunito — Google Fonts from DESIGN.md Section 3)\n60\t\n61\t| Style | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n62\t|---|---|---|---|---|\n63\t| `displayLarge` | 32sp | 700 | 40sp | Hero article title on featured card |\n64\t| `headlineMedium` | 22sp | 600 | 28sp | Section headers |\n65\t| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | 28sp | AppBar title |\n66\t| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | 24sp | Article card titles, topic card titles |\n67\t| `bodyLarge` | 16sp | 400 | 24sp | Primary body text, article descriptions |\n68\t| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | Secondary text, descriptions, card subtitles |\n69\t| `labelLarge` | 14sp | 600 | 20sp | Button text, chip labels |\n70\t| `caption` | 11sp | 500 | 16sp | Badges, timestamps, read time |\n71\t\n72\t### Spacing (8pt base from DESIGN.md Section 5 / UX.md Section 6)\n73\t\n74\t| Token | Value |\n75\t|---|---|\n76\t| `xxs` | 4dp |\n77\t| `xs` | 8dp |\n78\t| `sm` | 12dp |\n79\t| `md` | 16dp |\n80\t| `lg` | 24dp |\n81\t| `xl` | 32dp |\n82\t| `xxl` | 48dp |\n83\t\n84\t### Corner Radius\n85\t\n86\t| Token | Value |\n87\t|---|---|\n88\t| `sm` | 8dp (chips) |\n89\t| `md` | 12dp |\n90\t| `lg` | 16dp (standard cards, featured article card) |\n91\t| `full` | 999dp (FAB, pills) |\n92\t\n93\t### Motion (from DESIGN.md Section 6 / UX.md Section 6)\n94\t\n95\t| Token | Value |\n96\t|---|---|\n97\t| `durationShort` | 200ms |\n98\t| `durationMedium` | 300ms |\n99\t| `durationLong` | 350ms |\n100\t| `staggerDelay` | 50ms between items |\n101\t| `easingStandard` | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n102\t| `easingEnter` | `Curves.easeOut` |\n103\t| `easingExit` | `Curves.easeIn` |\n104\t\n105\t---\n106\t\n107\t## 6. Layout Rules\n108\t\n109\t### Scaffold Structure\n110\t\n111\t- `Scaffold` with `CustomScrollView` body (requires `SliverAppBar` for scroll behavior)\n112\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Education\", back button, trailing search icon button\n113\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden (per UX.md 3.8)\n114\t- `FAB`: None\n115\t\n116\t### AppBar Behavior\n117\t\n118\t- Background: `lavenderTint` (#F5F3FF) / Night Sky (#13111C) in dark mode\n119\t- Title: \"Education\" (SemiBold 20sp, `deepGraphite` / `softPearl` in dark mode)\n120\t- Leading: Back button with 48dp touch target\n121\t- Trailing: Search icon button (48dp touch target) to open search overlay\n122\t\n123\t### Body Layout\n124\t\n125\t- `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar` (collapsing header not needed — content scrolls beneath)\n126\t- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for Featured Article at top\n127\t- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for section header \"Topics\"\n128\t- `SliverGrid` for Topics (2 columns)\n129\t- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for section header \"Recent Articles\"\n130\t- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for Recent Articles (horizontal `ListView`)\n131\t- Bottom padding: 24dp for safe area\n132\t\n133\t---\n134\t\n135\t## 7. Sections\n136\t\n137\t### Section 1: Featured Article\n138\t\n139\t**Description:** Hero card at the top showcasing the current featured article with large image and headline.\n140\t\n141\t**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `Card`\n142\t\n143\t**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, stacked vertically (image top, content bottom).\n144\t\n145\t**Components:**\n146\t- Article hero image: Full-width, 180dp height, `radiusLg` top corners, placeholder gradient if no image\n147\t- Topic badge: Pill chip at top-left of image, `lavenderBloom` background\n148\t- Title: \"Featured Article\" prefix label (`caption`, `stoneGrey`) + Article title (`displayLarge` 32sp, `deepGraphite`)\n149\t- Read time: Clock icon + \"X min read\" (`caption`, `stoneGrey`)\n150\t- Tap entire card → `/article-reader/:id`\n151\t\n152\t**Card Specifications:**\n153\t- Background: `morningMist` (#FAFAFA) / `deepTwilight` in dark mode\n154\t- Corner radius: `radiusLg` (16dp)\n155\t- Shadow: Soft diffused — 8dp blur, 2dp offset-y, rgba(0,0,0,0.08) light / rgba(0,0,0,0.25) dark\n156\t- Internal padding: 16dp all sides\n157\t\n158\t**Data Requirements:**\n159\t- Static featured article from article catalog (for MVP)\n160\t- Fields: `id`, `title`, `topic`, `illustrationUrl`, `readTime`\n161\t\n162\t**Interactive Elements:**\n163\t- Tap card → push `/article-reader/:id`\n164\t\n165\t**Tap Feedback:** 200ms scale to 98% with 200ms return\n166\t\n167\t---\n168\t\n169\t### Section 2: Topics Grid\n170\t\n171\t**Description:** 2-column grid of topic category cards for filtering articles.\n172\t\n173\t**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `GridView` with `shrinkWrap: true` and `physics: NeverScrollableScrollPhysics()` OR separate `SliverGrid`\n174\t\n175\t**Layout:** 2 columns, 12dp gap between items, 16dp horizontal padding.\n176\t\n177\t**Topic Cards (5 total):**\n178\t1. **Nutrition** — Icon: `Icons.restaurant_outlined`, color: `lavenderBloom`\n179\t2. **Body Changes** — Icon: `Icons.pregnant_woman_outlined`, color: `blushRose`\n180\t3. **Maternal Care** — Icon: `Icons.medical_services_outlined`, color: `lavenderBloom`\n181\t4. **Exercise** — Icon: `Icons.fitness_center_outlined`, color: `softMint`\n182\t5. **Mental Health** — Icon: `Icons.psychology_outlined`, color: `blushRose`\n183\t\n184\t**Each Topic Card:**\n185\t- Size: Square-ish, aspect ratio ~1.3:1 (height slightly greater than width)\n186\t- Background: `morningMist` / `deepTwilight` in dark mode\n187\t- 48dp circular icon container at top with topic color at 15% opacity fill\n188\t- Icon: 24sp, topic color\n189\t- Title: Topic name (`titleMedium`, centered)\n190\t- Corner radius: `radiusLg` (16dp)\n191\t- Tap feedback: 200ms scale to 98%\n192\t\n193\t**Interactive Elements:**\n194\t- Tap topic card → `/education/:topic` (filtered article list)\n195\t\n196\t**Data Requirements:**\n197\t- Static topic list (for MVP)\n198\t- `ArticleTopic` enum: `nutrition`, `bodyChanges`, `maternalCare`, `exercise`, `mentalHealth`\n199\t\n200\t---\n201\t\n202\t### Section 3: Recent Articles\n203\t\n204\t**Description:** Horizontal scrollable list of recently viewed articles for quick re-access.\n205\t\n206\t**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `SizedBox` with horizontal `ListView`\n207\t\n208\t**Layout:** Horizontal scrolling `ListView` with `SizedBox` height ~220dp, 16dp horizontal padding.\n209\t\n210\t**Each Article Card:**\n211\t- Width: 160dp fixed\n212\t- Background: `morningMist` / `deepTwilight`\n213\t- Corner radius: `radiusLg` (16dp)\n214\t- Vertical stack:\n215\t  - Placeholder image area: 80dp height, `radiusSm` top corners, `lavenderTint` fill with centered icon\n216\t  - Title: `titleMedium`, max 2 lines, ellipsis overflow\n217\t  - Topic badge: Small pill below title\n218\t  - Read time: `caption` below topic badge\n219\t\n220\t**Interactive Elements:**\n221\t- Tap article card → `/article-reader/:id`\n222\t- Tap bookmark icon on card → toggle bookmark state\n223\t\n224\t**Data Requirements:**\n225\t- `ArticleProvider.articles` filtered for `isBookmarked == true` OR recently viewed (date-based)\n226\t\n227\t---\n228\t\n229\t### Section 4: Search Overlay\n230\t\n231\t**Description:** Full-screen overlay for searching articles by keyword.\n232\t\n233\t**Trigger:** Tap search icon in AppBar\n234\t\n235\t**Widget Type:** `showModalBottomSheet` with `Column` OR separate overlay route\n236\t\n237\t**Layout:** Bottom sheet or full-screen overlay with search input at top and results below.\n238\t\n239\t**Components:**\n240\t- Search input field: `TextField` with search icon prefix, clear button suffix\n241\t- Recent searches: List of recent search terms (tappable chips)\n242\t- Search results: Vertical list of `Article` cards matching query\n243\t- Empty state: \"No articles found\" with search icon\n244\t\n245\t**Data Operations:**\n246\t- On search submit: Filter `ArticleProvider.articles` by title/body containing query string\n247\t\n248\t---\n249\t\n250\t## 8. Data\n251\t\n252\t### Entity: Article\n253\t\n254\t| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n255\t|---|---|---|---|\n256\t| `id` | `String` (UUID) | Yes | Unique identifier |\n257\t| `title` | `String` | Yes | Article title |\n258\t| `topic` | `ArticleTopic` | Yes | Topic category for filtering |\n259\t| `body` | `String` | Yes | Rich text article content |\n260\t| `illustrationUrl` | `String` | No | Hero image URL |\n261\t| `readTime` | `String` | No | Estimated read time (e.g., \"5 min\") |\n262\t| `isBookmarked` | `bool` | Yes | Whether user has bookmarked this article |\n263\t| `relatedArticleIds` | `List<String>` | Yes | IDs of related articles shown at bottom |\n264\t\n265\t### Enum: ArticleTopic\n266\t\n267\t| Value | Display Name | Icon |\n268\t|---|---|---|\n269\t| `nutrition` | Nutrition | `Icons.restaurant_outlined` |\n270\t| `bodyChanges` | Body Changes | `Icons.pregnant_woman_outlined` |\n271\t| `maternalCare` | Maternal Care | `Icons.medical_services_outlined` |\n272\t| `exercise` | Exercise | `Icons.fitness_center_outlined` |\n273\t| `mentalHealth` | Mental Health | `Icons.psychology_outlined` |\n274\t\n275\t### Provider: ArticleProvider\n276\t\n277\t**State:**\n278\t- `articles: List<Article>` — all articles (static catalog for MVP)\n279\t- `bookmarkedIds: Set<String>` — IDs of bookmarked articles\n280\t- `recentSearches: List<String>` — recent search terms\n281\t\n282\t**Methods:**\n283\t- `getArticlesByTopic(topic)` — filters articles by `ArticleTopic`\n284\t- `toggleBookmark(id)` — toggles `isBookmarked` state\n285\t- `searchArticles(query)` — filters by title/body containing query\n286\t- `getBookmarkedArticles()` — returns articles where `isBookmarked == true`\n287\t- `getRecentArticles()` — returns recently viewed (by date, limit 5-10)\n288\t\n289\t---\n290\t\n291\t## 9. Motion\n292\t\n293\t### Entry Animations\n294\t\n295\t- Screen push: 300ms slide + fade (standard page transition)\n296\t- Featured article card: 200ms fade-in on load\n297\t- Topic grid: Staggered reveal — each card fades in 50ms apart\n298\t- Recent articles: Horizontal slide-in from right, 300ms\n299\t\n300\t### Hero Transitions\n301\t\n302\t- When navigating from article card to Article Reader: 350ms fast-out-slow-in shared element transition on card image and title\n303\t\n304\t### Bottom Sheet Animations\n305\t\n306\t- Search overlay: 250ms smooth deceleration slide-up\n307\t- Sheet dismiss: 200ms slide-down with fade\n308\t\n309\t### Interactive Feedback\n310\t\n311\t- Card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%, then 200ms ease-out return\n312\t- Topic card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%\n313\t- Bookmark icon tap: 150ms scale bounce + color transition\n314\t- Search input focus: 200ms border color transition to `lavenderBloom`\n315\t\n316\t### Staggered List Reveals\n317\t\n318\t- When content loads: list items cascade into view — 50ms delay between each item\n319\t- Applies to topic grid (items appear 50ms apart)\n320\t\n321\t---\n322\t\n323\t## 10. Accessibility\n324\t\n325\t### Semantic Labels\n326\t\n327\t| Element | Semantic Label |\n328\t|---|---|\n329\t| AppBar | `'Education, back button to return to Library, search button'` |\n330\t| Search button | `'Search articles, double tap to search'` |\n331\t| Featured article | `'$articleTitle, featured article, $readTime to read, double tap to open'` |\n332\t| Topic card | `'$topicName, double tap to view $topicName articles'` |\n333\t| Recent article | `'$articleTitle, $topicName, $readTime, double tap to read'` |\n334\t| Bookmark icon | `'Bookmark article, ${isBookmarked ? 'bookmarked' : 'not bookmarked'}'` |\n335\t| Read time | `'$readTime to read'` |\n336\t\n337\t### Focus Order\n338\t\n339\t1. AppBar (back button → search button)\n340\t2. Featured article card\n341\t3. Topic cards (in grid order: Nutrition, Body Changes, Maternal Care, Exercise, Mental Health)\n342\t4. Recent article horizontal list (left to right)\n343\t5. Within each recent article: bookmark icon\n344\t\n345\t### Contrast Notes\n346\t\n347\t- `lavenderBloom` on `morningMist`: ~5.2:1 (passes AA)\n348\t- `deepGraphite` on `morningMist`: ~12:1 (passes AAA)\n349\t- `stoneGrey` on `morningMist`: ~4.7:1 (passes AA for body text)\n350\t- Dark mode: `twilightBloom` on `deepTwilight`: ~5.8:1 (passes AA)\n351\t\n352\t### Screen Reader Support\n353\t\n354\t- Announce article opened: \"Opening article: $title\"\n355\t- Announce bookmark toggled: \"Article ${isBookmarked ? 'bookmarked' : 'bookmark removed'}\"\n356\t- Announce search results: \"Found $count articles matching '$query'\"\n357\t- Use `Semantics` to label topic cards with topic name and article count if available\n358\t\n359\t### Touch Target Compliance\n360\t\n361\t- All interactive elements: 48dp minimum\n362\t- Topic cards: Full card area, minimum 48dp height\n363\t- Recent article cards: Full card area, 160dp width\n364\t- Bookmark icons: 48dp minimum touch target area (extends tappable area beyond icon itself)\n365\t- All buttons in AppBar: 48dp minimum height\n366\t\n367\t---\n368\t\n369\t## 11. Anti-Patterns\n370\t\n371\t**Do Not:**\n372\t- Add `BottomNavigationBar` (hidden per UX spec)\n373\t- Add FAB (Education screen has no primary action requiring FAB)\n374\t- Use `GridView` for recent articles (use horizontal `ListView` for horizontal scrolling)\n375\t- Add gradients to card backgrounds (flat `morningMist` only)\n376\t- Use platform default colors (all colors from design system)\n377\t- Use Inter, Roboto, or any font other than Nunito\n378\t- Create touch targets smaller than 48dp\n379\t- Use pure black (#000000) or pure white (#FFFFFF) for text\n380\t- Show featured article with hard-coded content in production (use provider data)\n381\t- Use `Navigator.push` instead of `context.push` with GoRouter\n382\t- Skip safe area handling\n383\t- Display empty state without illustration/guidance text\n384\t- Add shadows to AppBar (transparent/floating style per design system)\n385\t- Use default `Material` tap ripple — use scale feedback per design system\n386\t- Show all articles in recent if none are bookmarked — show \"no recent articles\" state\n387\t\n388\t---\n389\t\n390\t## 12. Critical Files for Implementation\n391\t\n392\t1. **`lib/screens/education/education_screen.dart`** — New file to create (main scaffold with CustomScrollView, AppBar with search, sections for Featured Article, Topics Grid, Recent Articles)\n393\t\n394\t2. **`lib/router/app_router.dart`** — Add GoRoute entry for `/education` pointing to `EducationScreen` and `/education/:topic` for topic-filtered article list\n395\t\n396\t3. **`lib/theme/app_theme.dart`** — Reference for design tokens (`AppTheme.spaceMd`, `AppTheme.radiusLg`, `AppTheme.lavenderBloom`, etc.) and typography via `Theme.of(context).textTheme`\n397\t\n398\t4. **`lib/screens/health_log/health_log_screen.dart`** — Reference implementation for a push-screen with `Scaffold`, `AppBar`, `ListView`/`CustomScrollView` body, card-based content with proper spacing and scale feedback patterns\n399\t\n400\t5. **`.stitch/UX.md` (Section 3.8)** — Reference for Education screen specification: scaffold structure (AppBar with search, hidden BottomNav, no FAB), sections (featured article, topics grid, recent articles), data requirements (`ArticleProvider`), and interaction patterns\n401\t\n402\t---\n403\t\n404\t## 13. Screen Structure\n405\t\n406\t```\n407\tEducationScreen\n408\t├── Scaffold\n409\t│   ├── AppBar (\"Education\", back button, search icon)\n410\t│   └── body: CustomScrollView\n411\t│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n412\t│       │   └── FeaturedArticleCard\n413\t│       │       ├── Hero image\n414\t│       │       ├── Topic badge\n415\t│       │       └── Content (title, read time)\n416\t│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n417\t│       │   └── SectionHeader(\"Topics\")\n418\t│       ├── SliverGrid (2 columns)\n419\t│       │   └── TopicCard × 5 (Nutrition, Body Changes, Maternal Care, Exercise, Mental Health)\n420\t│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n421\t│       │   └── SectionHeader(\"Recent Articles\")\n422\t│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n423\t│       │   └── RecentArticlesList (horizontal ListView)\n424\t│       │       └── ArticleCard × N\n425\t│       └── SliverToBoxAdapter (bottom padding)\n426\t├── Search icon → SearchOverlay\n427\t└── Topic card tap → /education/:topic\n428\t```"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f7a94ff0-43d7-45a8-89c7-107b23773d5e","uuid":"cfc2a67e-edd7-4b34-bb3a-1c99cfe7c117","timestamp":"2026-05-19T01:39:12.513Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.stitch/designs/education/SPEC.md","content":"# Education — Screen Specification\n\n## 1. Screen Title\n\n**Education**\n\n---\n\n## 2. Purpose\n\nBrowse and read trusted educational articles organized by topic. This screen serves as a content discovery hub, allowing users to explore curated health information relevant to their pregnancy journey. Users can filter by topic, search articles, and bookmark content for later reference.\n\n**Context:** Push route from Library tab. BottomNavigationBar is hidden. Primary actions are topic filtering, search, and article navigation.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Route\n\n`/education`\n\n---\n\n## 4. Widget Name\n\n`EducationScreen`\n\n---\n\n## 5. Design Tokens\n\n### Colors (Light Theme — from DESIGN.md Section 2)\n\n| Token | Hex | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary brand, AppBar, topic icons (Nutrition, Maternal Care) |\n| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n| `blushRose` | `#F9A8D4` | Secondary accent, Mental Health topic icon |\n| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Tertiary, success states, bookmark active indicator |\n| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text |\n| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, captions, timestamps |\n| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | Borders, dividers |\n| `softCoral` | `#EF4444` | Error states |\n| `warmWhite` | `#FFFFFF` | Bottom nav background, sheets |\n\n### Colors (Dark Theme)\n\n| Token | Hex | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `twilightBloom` | `#9F67FF` | Primary brand in dark mode |\n| `duskyRose` | `#FBC4E0` | Secondary accent in dark mode |\n| `nightMint` | `#34D399` | Tertiary success in dark mode |\n| `deepTwilight` | `#1E1B2E` | Card backgrounds in dark mode |\n| `nightSky` | `#13111C` | Scaffold background in dark mode |\n| `softPearl` | `#F3F4F6` | Primary text in dark mode |\n| `mutedSilver` | `#9CA3AF` | Secondary text in dark mode |\n| `deepBorder` | `#2D2B3A` | Borders in dark mode |\n\n### Typography (Nunito — Google Fonts from DESIGN.md Section 3)\n\n| Style | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| `displayLarge` | 32sp | 700 | 40sp | Hero article title on featured card |\n| `headlineMedium` | 22sp | 600 | 28sp | Section headers |\n| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | 28sp | AppBar title |\n| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | 24sp | Article card titles, topic card titles |\n| `bodyLarge` | 16sp | 400 | 24sp | Primary body text, article descriptions |\n| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | Secondary text, descriptions, card subtitles |\n| `labelLarge` | 14sp | 600 | 20sp | Button text, chip labels |\n| `caption` | 11sp | 500 | 16sp | Badges, timestamps, read time |\n\n### Spacing (8pt base from DESIGN.md Section 5 / UX.md Section 6)\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `xxs` | 4dp |\n| `xs` | 8dp |\n| `sm` | 12dp |\n| `md` | 16dp |\n| `lg` | 24dp |\n| `xl` | 32dp |\n| `xxl` | 48dp |\n\n### Corner Radius\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `sm` | 8dp (chips) |\n| `md` | 12dp |\n| `lg` | 16dp (standard cards, featured article card) |\n| `full` | 999dp (FAB, pills) |\n\n### Motion (from DESIGN.md Section 6 / UX.md Section 6)\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `durationShort` | 200ms |\n| `durationMedium` | 300ms |\n| `durationLong` | 350ms |\n| `staggerDelay` | 50ms between items |\n| `easingStandard` | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n| `easingEnter` | `Curves.easeOut` |\n| `easingExit` | `Curves.easeIn` |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Layout Rules\n\n### Scaffold Structure\n\n- `Scaffold` with `CustomScrollView` body (requires `SliverAppBar` for scroll behavior)\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Education\", back button, trailing search icon button\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden (per UX.md 3.8)\n- `FAB`: None\n\n### AppBar Behavior\n\n- Background: `lavenderTint` (#F5F3FF) / Night Sky (#13111C) in dark mode\n- Title: \"Education\" (SemiBold 20sp, `deepGraphite` / `softPearl` in dark mode)\n- Leading: Back button with 48dp touch target\n- Trailing: Search icon button (48dp touch target) to open search overlay\n\n### Body Layout\n\n- `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar` (collapsing header not needed — content scrolls beneath)\n- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for Featured Article at top\n- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for section header \"Topics\"\n- `SliverGrid` for Topics (2 columns)\n- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for section header \"Recent Articles\"\n- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for Recent Articles (horizontal `ListView`)\n- Bottom padding: 24dp for safe area\n\n---\n\n## 7. Sections\n\n### Section 1: Featured Article\n\n**Description:** Hero card at the top showcasing the current featured article with large image and headline.\n\n**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `Card`\n\n**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, stacked vertically (image top, content bottom).\n\n**Components:**\n- Article hero image: Full-width, 180dp height, `radiusLg` top corners, placeholder gradient if no image\n- Topic badge: Pill chip at top-left of image, `lavenderBloom` background\n- Title: \"Featured Article\" prefix label (`caption`, `stoneGrey`) + Article title (`displayLarge` 32sp, `deepGraphite`)\n- Read time: Clock icon + \"X min read\" (`caption`, `stoneGrey`)\n- Tap entire card → `/article-reader/:id`\n\n**Card Specifications:**\n- Background: `morningMist` (#FAFAFA) / `deepTwilight` in dark mode\n- Corner radius: `radiusLg` (16dp)\n- Shadow: Soft diffused — 8dp blur, 2dp offset-y, rgba(0,0,0,0.08) light / rgba(0,0,0,0.25) dark\n- Internal padding: 16dp all sides\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- Static featured article from article catalog (for MVP)\n- Fields: `id`, `title`, `topic`, `illustrationUrl`, `readTime`\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap card → push `/article-reader/:id`\n\n**Tap Feedback:** 200ms scale to 98% with 200ms return\n\n---\n\n### Section 2: Topics Grid\n\n**Description:** 2-column grid of topic category cards for filtering articles.\n\n**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `GridView` with `shrinkWrap: true` and `physics: NeverScrollableScrollPhysics()` OR separate `SliverGrid`\n\n**Layout:** 2 columns, 12dp gap between items, 16dp horizontal padding.\n\n**Topic Cards (5 total):**\n1. **Nutrition** — Icon: `Icons.restaurant_outlined`, color: `lavenderBloom`\n2. **Body Changes** — Icon: `Icons.pregnant_woman_outlined`, color: `blushRose`\n3. **Maternal Care** — Icon: `Icons.medical_services_outlined`, color: `lavenderBloom`\n4. **Exercise** — Icon: `Icons.fitness_center_outlined`, color: `softMint`\n5. **Mental Health** — Icon: `Icons.psychology_outlined`, color: `blushRose`\n\n**Each Topic Card:**\n- Size: Square-ish, aspect ratio ~1.3:1 (height slightly greater than width)\n- Background: `morningMist` / `deepTwilight` in dark mode\n- 48dp circular icon container at top with topic color at 15% opacity fill\n- Icon: 24sp, topic color\n- Title: Topic name (`titleMedium`, centered)\n- Corner radius: `radiusLg` (16dp)\n- Tap feedback: 200ms scale to 98%\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap topic card → `/education/:topic` (filtered article list)\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- Static topic list (for MVP)\n- `ArticleTopic` enum: `nutrition`, `bodyChanges`, `maternalCare`, `exercise`, `mentalHealth`\n\n---\n\n### Section 3: Recent Articles\n\n**Description:** Horizontal scrollable list of recently viewed articles for quick re-access.\n\n**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `SizedBox` with horizontal `ListView`\n\n**Layout:** Horizontal scrolling `ListView` with `SizedBox` height ~220dp, 16dp horizontal padding.\n\n**Each Article Card:**\n- Width: 160dp fixed\n- Background: `morningMist` / `deepTwilight`\n- Corner radius: `radiusLg` (16dp)\n- Vertical stack:\n  - Placeholder image area: 80dp height, `radiusSm` top corners, `lavenderTint` fill with centered icon\n  - Title: `titleMedium`, max 2 lines, ellipsis overflow\n  - Topic badge: Small pill below title\n  - Read time: `caption` below topic badge\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap article card → `/article-reader/:id`\n- Tap bookmark icon on card → toggle bookmark state\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- `ArticleProvider.articles` filtered for `isBookmarked == true` OR recently viewed (date-based)\n\n---\n\n### Section 4: Search Overlay\n\n**Description:** Full-screen overlay for searching articles by keyword.\n\n**Trigger:** Tap search icon in AppBar\n\n**Widget Type:** `showModalBottomSheet` with `Column` OR separate overlay route\n\n**Layout:** Bottom sheet or full-screen overlay with search input at top and results below.\n\n**Components:**\n- Search input field: `TextField` with search icon prefix, clear button suffix\n- Recent searches: List of recent search terms (tappable chips)\n- Search results: Vertical list of `Article` cards matching query\n- Empty state: \"No articles found\" with search icon\n\n**Data Operations:**\n- On search submit: Filter `ArticleProvider.articles` by title/body containing query string\n\n---\n\n## 8. Data\n\n### Entity: Article\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `id` | `String` (UUID) | Yes | Unique identifier |\n| `title` | `String` | Yes | Article title |\n| `topic` | `ArticleTopic` | Yes | Topic category for filtering |\n| `body` | `String` | Yes | Rich text article content |\n| `illustrationUrl` | `String` | No | Hero image URL |\n| `readTime` | `String` | No | Estimated read time (e.g., \"5 min\") |\n| `isBookmarked` | `bool` | Yes | Whether user has bookmarked this article |\n| `relatedArticleIds` | `List<String>` | Yes | IDs of related articles shown at bottom |\n\n### Enum: ArticleTopic\n\n| Value | Display Name | Icon |\n|---|---|---|\n| `nutrition` | Nutrition | `Icons.restaurant_outlined` |\n| `bodyChanges` | Body Changes | `Icons.pregnant_woman_outlined` |\n| `maternalCare` | Maternal Care | `Icons.medical_services_outlined` |\n| `exercise` | Exercise | `Icons.fitness_center_outlined` |\n| `mentalHealth` | Mental Health | `Icons.psychology_outlined` |\n\n### Provider: ArticleProvider\n\n**State:**\n- `articles: List<Article>` — all articles (static catalog for MVP)\n- `bookmarkedIds: Set<String>` — IDs of bookmarked articles\n- `recentSearches: List<String>` — recent search terms\n\n**Methods:**\n- `getArticlesByTopic(topic)` — filters articles by `ArticleTopic`\n- `toggleBookmark(id)` — toggles `isBookmarked` state\n- `searchArticles(query)` — filters by title/body containing query\n- `getBookmarkedArticles()` — returns articles where `isBookmarked == true`\n- `getRecentArticles()` — returns recently viewed (by date, limit 5-10)\n\n---\n\n## 9. Motion\n\n### Entry Animations\n\n- Screen push: 300ms slide + fade (standard page transition)\n- Featured article card: 200ms fade-in on load\n- Topic grid: Staggered reveal — each card fades in 50ms apart\n- Recent articles: Horizontal slide-in from right, 300ms\n\n### Hero Transitions\n\n- When navigating from article card to Article Reader: 350ms fast-out-slow-in shared element transition on card image and title\n\n### Bottom Sheet Animations\n\n- Search overlay: 250ms smooth deceleration slide-up\n- Sheet dismiss: 200ms slide-down with fade\n\n### Interactive Feedback\n\n- Card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%, then 200ms ease-out return\n- Topic card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%\n- Bookmark icon tap: 150ms scale bounce + color transition\n- Search input focus: 200ms border color transition to `lavenderBloom`\n\n### Staggered List Reveals\n\n- When content loads: list items cascade into view — 50ms delay between each item\n- Applies to topic grid (items appear 50ms apart)\n\n---\n\n## 10. Accessibility\n\n### Semantic Labels\n\n| Element | Semantic Label |\n|---|---|\n| AppBar | `'Education, back button to return to Library, search button'` |\n| Search button | `'Search articles, double tap to search'` |\n| Featured article | `'$articleTitle, featured article, $readTime to read, double tap to open'` |\n| Topic card | `'$topicName, double tap to view $topicName articles'` |\n| Recent article | `'$articleTitle, $topicName, $readTime, double tap to read'` |\n| Bookmark icon | `'Bookmark article, ${isBookmarked ? 'bookmarked' : 'not bookmarked'}'` |\n| Read time | `'$readTime to read'` |\n\n### Focus Order\n\n1. AppBar (back button → search button)\n2. Featured article card\n3. Topic cards (in grid order: Nutrition, Body Changes, Maternal Care, Exercise, Mental Health)\n4. Recent article horizontal list (left to right)\n5. Within each recent article: bookmark icon\n\n### Contrast Notes\n\n- `lavenderBloom` on `morningMist`: ~5.2:1 (passes AA)\n- `deepGraphite` on `morningMist`: ~12:1 (passes AAA)\n- `stoneGrey` on `morningMist`: ~4.7:1 (passes AA for body text)\n- Dark mode: `twilightBloom` on `deepTwilight`: ~5.8:1 (passes AA)\n\n### Screen Reader Support\n\n- Announce article opened: \"Opening article: $title\"\n- Announce bookmark toggled: \"Article ${isBookmarked ? 'bookmarked' : 'bookmark removed'}\"\n- Announce search results: \"Found $count articles matching '$query'\"\n- Use `Semantics` to label topic cards with topic name and article count if available\n\n### Touch Target Compliance\n\n- All interactive elements: 48dp minimum\n- Topic cards: Full card area, minimum 48dp height\n- Recent article cards: Full card area, 160dp width\n- Bookmark icons: 48dp minimum touch target area (extends tappable area beyond icon itself)\n- All buttons in AppBar: 48dp minimum height\n\n---\n\n## 11. Anti-Patterns\n\n**Do Not:**\n- Add `BottomNavigationBar` (hidden per UX spec)\n- Add FAB (Education screen has no primary action requiring FAB)\n- Use `GridView` for recent articles (use horizontal `ListView` for horizontal scrolling)\n- Add gradients to card backgrounds (flat `morningMist` only)\n- Use platform default colors (all colors from design system)\n- Use Inter, Roboto, or any font other than Nunito\n- Create touch targets smaller than 48dp\n- Use pure black (#000000) or pure white (#FFFFFF) for text\n- Show featured article with hard-coded content in production (use provider data)\n- Use `Navigator.push` instead of `context.push` with GoRouter\n- Skip safe area handling\n- Display empty state without illustration/guidance text\n- Add shadows to AppBar (transparent/floating style per design system)\n- Use default `Material` tap ripple — use scale feedback per design system\n- Show all articles in recent if none are bookmarked — show \"no recent articles\" state\n\n---\n\n## 12. Critical Files for Implementation\n\n1. **`lib/screens/education/education_screen.dart`** — New file to create (main scaffold with CustomScrollView, AppBar with search, sections for Featured Article, Topics Grid, Recent Articles)\n\n2. **`lib/router/app_router.dart`** — Add GoRoute entry for `/education` pointing to `EducationScreen` and `/education/:topic` for topic-filtered article list\n\n3. **`lib/theme/app_theme.dart`** — Reference for design tokens (`AppTheme.spaceMd`, `AppTheme.radiusLg`, `AppTheme.lavenderBloom`, etc.) and typography via `Theme.of(context).textTheme`\n\n4. **`lib/screens/health_log/health_log_screen.dart`** — Reference implementation for a push-screen with `Scaffold`, `AppBar`, `ListView`/`CustomScrollView` body, card-based content with proper spacing and scale feedback patterns\n\n5. **`.stitch/UX.md` (Section 3.8)** — Reference for Education screen specification: scaffold structure (AppBar with search, hidden BottomNav, no FAB), sections (featured article, topics grid, recent articles), data requirements (`ArticleProvider`), and interaction patterns\n\n---\n\n## 13. Screen Structure\n\n```\nEducationScreen\n├── Scaffold\n│   ├── AppBar (\"Education\", back button, search icon)\n│   └── body: CustomScrollView\n│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n│       │   └── FeaturedArticleCard\n│       │       ├── Hero image\n│       │       ├── Topic badge\n│       │       └── Content (title, read time)\n│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n│       │   └── SectionHeader(\"Topics\")\n│       ├── SliverGrid (2 columns)\n│       │   └── TopicCard × 5 (Nutrition, Body Changes, Maternal Care, Exercise, Mental Health)\n│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n│       │   └── SectionHeader(\"Recent Articles\")\n│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n│       │   └── RecentArticlesList (horizontal ListView)\n│       │       └── ArticleCard × N\n│       └── SliverToBoxAdapter (bottom padding)\n├── Search icon → SearchOverlay\n└── Topic card tap → /education/:topic\n```","numLines":428,"startLine":1,"totalLines":428}}}
[2026-05-19T01:39:12.514Z] [STREAM_EVENT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_h0jsjtcat0t0_1","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Education — Screen Specification\n2\t\n3\t## 1. Screen Title\n4\t\n5\t**Education**\n6\t\n7\t---\n8\t\n9\t## 2. Purpose\n10\t\n11\tBrowse and read trusted educational articles organized by topic. This screen serves as a content discovery hub, allowing users to explore curated health information relevant to their pregnancy journey. Users can filter by topic, search articles, and bookmark content for later reference.\n12\t\n13\t**Context:** Push route from Library tab. BottomNavigationBar is hidden. Primary actions are topic filtering, search, and article navigation.\n14\t\n15\t---\n16\t\n17\t## 3. Route\n18\t\n19\t`/education`\n20\t\n21\t---\n22\t\n23\t## 4. Widget Name\n24\t\n25\t`EducationScreen`\n26\t\n27\t---\n28\t\n29\t## 5. Design Tokens\n30\t\n31\t### Colors (Light Theme — from DESIGN.md Section 2)\n32\t\n33\t| Token | Hex | Usage |\n34\t|---|---|---|\n35\t| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary brand, AppBar, topic icons (Nutrition, Maternal Care) |\n36\t| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n37\t| `blushRose` | `#F9A8D4` | Secondary accent, Mental Health topic icon |\n38\t| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Tertiary, success states, bookmark active indicator |\n39\t| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n40\t| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text |\n41\t| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, captions, timestamps |\n42\t| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | Borders, dividers |\n43\t| `softCoral` | `#EF4444` | Error states |\n44\t| `warmWhite` | `#FFFFFF` | Bottom nav background, sheets |\n45\t\n46\t### Colors (Dark Theme)\n47\t\n48\t| Token | Hex | Usage |\n49\t|---|---|---|\n50\t| `twilightBloom` | `#9F67FF` | Primary brand in dark mode |\n51\t| `duskyRose` | `#FBC4E0` | Secondary accent in dark mode |\n52\t| `nightMint` | `#34D399` | Tertiary success in dark mode |\n53\t| `deepTwilight` | `#1E1B2E` | Card backgrounds in dark mode |\n54\t| `nightSky` | `#13111C` | Scaffold background in dark mode |\n55\t| `softPearl` | `#F3F4F6` | Primary text in dark mode |\n56\t| `mutedSilver` | `#9CA3AF` | Secondary text in dark mode |\n57\t| `deepBorder` | `#2D2B3A` | Borders in dark mode |\n58\t\n59\t### Typography (Nunito — Google Fonts from DESIGN.md Section 3)\n60\t\n61\t| Style | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n62\t|---|---|---|---|---|\n63\t| `displayLarge` | 32sp | 700 | 40sp | Hero article title on featured card |\n64\t| `headlineMedium` | 22sp | 600 | 28sp | Section headers |\n65\t| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | 28sp | AppBar title |\n66\t| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | 24sp | Article card titles, topic card titles |\n67\t| `bodyLarge` | 16sp | 400 | 24sp | Primary body text, article descriptions |\n68\t| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | Secondary text, descriptions, card subtitles |\n69\t| `labelLarge` | 14sp | 600 | 20sp | Button text, chip labels |\n70\t| `caption` | 11sp | 500 | 16sp | Badges, timestamps, read time |\n71\t\n72\t### Spacing (8pt base from DESIGN.md Section 5 / UX.md Section 6)\n73\t\n74\t| Token | Value |\n75\t|---|---|\n76\t| `xxs` | 4dp |\n77\t| `xs` | 8dp |\n78\t| `sm` | 12dp |\n79\t| `md` | 16dp |\n80\t| `lg` | 24dp |\n81\t| `xl` | 32dp |\n82\t| `xxl` | 48dp |\n83\t\n84\t### Corner Radius\n85\t\n86\t| Token | Value |\n87\t|---|---|\n88\t| `sm` | 8dp (chips) |\n89\t| `md` | 12dp |\n90\t| `lg` | 16dp (standard cards, featured article card) |\n91\t| `full` | 999dp (FAB, pills) |\n92\t\n93\t### Motion (from DESIGN.md Section 6 / UX.md Section 6)\n94\t\n95\t| Token | Value |\n96\t|---|---|\n97\t| `durationShort` | 200ms |\n98\t| `durationMedium` | 300ms |\n99\t| `durationLong` | 350ms |\n100\t| `staggerDelay` | 50ms between items |\n101\t| `easingStandard` | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n102\t| `easingEnter` | `Curves.easeOut` |\n103\t| `easingExit` | `Curves.easeIn` |\n104\t\n105\t---\n106\t\n107\t## 6. Layout Rules\n108\t\n109\t### Scaffold Structure\n110\t\n111\t- `Scaffold` with `CustomScrollView` body (requires `SliverAppBar` for scroll behavior)\n112\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Education\", back button, trailing search icon button\n113\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden (per UX.md 3.8)\n114\t- `FAB`: None\n115\t\n116\t### AppBar Behavior\n117\t\n118\t- Background: `lavenderTint` (#F5F3FF) / Night Sky (#13111C) in dark mode\n119\t- Title: \"Education\" (SemiBold 20sp, `deepGraphite` / `softPearl` in dark mode)\n120\t- Leading: Back button with 48dp touch target\n121\t- Trailing: Search icon button (48dp touch target) to open search overlay\n122\t\n123\t### Body Layout\n124\t\n125\t- `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar` (collapsing header not needed — content scrolls beneath)\n126\t- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for Featured Article at top\n127\t- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for section header \"Topics\"\n128\t- `SliverGrid` for Topics (2 columns)\n129\t- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for section header \"Recent Articles\"\n130\t- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for Recent Articles (horizontal `ListView`)\n131\t- Bottom padding: 24dp for safe area\n132\t\n133\t---\n134\t\n135\t## 7. Sections\n136\t\n137\t### Section 1: Featured Article\n138\t\n139\t**Description:** Hero card at the top showcasing the current featured article with large image and headline.\n140\t\n141\t**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `Card`\n142\t\n143\t**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, stacked vertically (image top, content bottom).\n144\t\n145\t**Components:**\n146\t- Article hero image: Full-width, 180dp height, `radiusLg` top corners, placeholder gradient if no image\n147\t- Topic badge: Pill chip at top-left of image, `lavenderBloom` background\n148\t- Title: \"Featured Article\" prefix label (`caption`, `stoneGrey`) + Article title (`displayLarge` 32sp, `deepGraphite`)\n149\t- Read time: Clock icon + \"X min read\" (`caption`, `stoneGrey`)\n150\t- Tap entire card → `/article-reader/:id`\n151\t\n152\t**Card Specifications:**\n153\t- Background: `morningMist` (#FAFAFA) / `deepTwilight` in dark mode\n154\t- Corner radius: `radiusLg` (16dp)\n155\t- Shadow: Soft diffused — 8dp blur, 2dp offset-y, rgba(0,0,0,0.08) light / rgba(0,0,0,0.25) dark\n156\t- Internal padding: 16dp all sides\n157\t\n158\t**Data Requirements:**\n159\t- Static featured article from article catalog (for MVP)\n160\t- Fields: `id`, `title`, `topic`, `illustrationUrl`, `readTime`\n161\t\n162\t**Interactive Elements:**\n163\t- Tap card → push `/article-reader/:id`\n164\t\n165\t**Tap Feedback:** 200ms scale to 98% with 200ms return\n166\t\n167\t---\n168\t\n169\t### Section 2: Topics Grid\n170\t\n171\t**Description:** 2-column grid of topic category cards for filtering articles.\n172\t\n173\t**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `GridView` with `shrinkWrap: true` and `physics: NeverScrollableScrollPhysics()` OR separate `SliverGrid`\n174\t\n175\t**Layout:** 2 columns, 12dp gap between items, 16dp horizontal padding.\n176\t\n177\t**Topic Cards (5 total):**\n178\t1. **Nutrition** — Icon: `Icons.restaurant_outlined`, color: `lavenderBloom`\n179\t2. **Body Changes** — Icon: `Icons.pregnant_woman_outlined`, color: `blushRose`\n180\t3. **Maternal Care** — Icon: `Icons.medical_services_outlined`, color: `lavenderBloom`\n181\t4. **Exercise** — Icon: `Icons.fitness_center_outlined`, color: `softMint`\n182\t5. **Mental Health** — Icon: `Icons.psychology_outlined`, color: `blushRose`\n183\t\n184\t**Each Topic Card:**\n185\t- Size: Square-ish, aspect ratio ~1.3:1 (height slightly greater than width)\n186\t- Background: `morningMist` / `deepTwilight` in dark mode\n187\t- 48dp circular icon container at top with topic color at 15% opacity fill\n188\t- Icon: 24sp, topic color\n189\t- Title: Topic name (`titleMedium`, centered)\n190\t- Corner radius: `radiusLg` (16dp)\n191\t- Tap feedback: 200ms scale to 98%\n192\t\n193\t**Interactive Elements:**\n194\t- Tap topic card → `/education/:topic` (filtered article list)\n195\t\n196\t**Data Requirements:**\n197\t- Static topic list (for MVP)\n198\t- `ArticleTopic` enum: `nutrition`, `bodyChanges`, `maternalCare`, `exercise`, `mentalHealth`\n199\t\n200\t---\n201\t\n202\t### Section 3: Recent Articles\n203\t\n204\t**Description:** Horizontal scrollable list of recently viewed articles for quick re-access.\n205\t\n206\t**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `SizedBox` with horizontal `ListView`\n207\t\n208\t**Layout:** Horizontal scrolling `ListView` with `SizedBox` height ~220dp, 16dp horizontal padding.\n209\t\n210\t**Each Article Card:**\n211\t- Width: 160dp fixed\n212\t- Background: `morningMist` / `deepTwilight`\n213\t- Corner radius: `radiusLg` (16dp)\n214\t- Vertical stack:\n215\t  - Placeholder image area: 80dp height, `radiusSm` top corners, `lavenderTint` fill with centered icon\n216\t  - Title: `titleMedium`, max 2 lines, ellipsis overflow\n217\t  - Topic badge: Small pill below title\n218\t  - Read time: `caption` below topic badge\n219\t\n220\t**Interactive Elements:**\n221\t- Tap article card → `/article-reader/:id`\n222\t- Tap bookmark icon on card → toggle bookmark state\n223\t\n224\t**Data Requirements:**\n225\t- `ArticleProvider.articles` filtered for `isBookmarked == true` OR recently viewed (date-based)\n226\t\n227\t---\n228\t\n229\t### Section 4: Search Overlay\n230\t\n231\t**Description:** Full-screen overlay for searching articles by keyword.\n232\t\n233\t**Trigger:** Tap search icon in AppBar\n234\t\n235\t**Widget Type:** `showModalBottomSheet` with `Column` OR separate overlay route\n236\t\n237\t**Layout:** Bottom sheet or full-screen overlay with search input at top and results below.\n238\t\n239\t**Components:**\n240\t- Search input field: `TextField` with search icon prefix, clear button suffix\n241\t- Recent searches: List of recent search terms (tappable chips)\n242\t- Search results: Vertical list of `Article` cards matching query\n243\t- Empty state: \"No articles found\" with search icon\n244\t\n245\t**Data Operations:**\n246\t- On search submit: Filter `ArticleProvider.articles` by title/body containing query string\n247\t\n248\t---\n249\t\n250\t## 8. Data\n251\t\n252\t### Entity: Article\n253\t\n254\t| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n255\t|---|---|---|---|\n256\t| `id` | `String` (UUID) | Yes | Unique identifier |\n257\t| `title` | `String` | Yes | Article title |\n258\t| `topic` | `ArticleTopic` | Yes | Topic category for filtering |\n259\t| `body` | `String` | Yes | Rich text article content |\n260\t| `illustrationUrl` | `String` | No | Hero image URL |\n261\t| `readTime` | `String` | No | Estimated read time (e.g., \"5 min\") |\n262\t| `isBookmarked` | `bool` | Yes | Whether user has bookmarked this article |\n263\t| `relatedArticleIds` | `List<String>` | Yes | IDs of related articles shown at bottom |\n264\t\n265\t### Enum: ArticleTopic\n266\t\n267\t| Value | Display Name | Icon |\n268\t|---|---|---|\n269\t| `nutrition` | Nutrition | `Icons.restaurant_outlined` |\n270\t| `bodyChanges` | Body Changes | `Icons.pregnant_woman_outlined` |\n271\t| `maternalCare` | Maternal Care | `Icons.medical_services_outlined` |\n272\t| `exercise` | Exercise | `Icons.fitness_center_outlined` |\n273\t| `mentalHealth` | Mental Health | `Icons.psychology_outlined` |\n274\t\n275\t### Provider: ArticleProvider\n276\t\n277\t**State:**\n278\t- `articles: List<Article>` — all articles (static catalog for MVP)\n279\t- `bookmarkedIds: Set<String>` — IDs of bookmarked articles\n280\t- `recentSearches: List<String>` — recent search terms\n281\t\n282\t**Methods:**\n283\t- `getArticlesByTopic(topic)` — filters articles by `ArticleTopic`\n284\t- `toggleBookmark(id)` — toggles `isBookmarked` state\n285\t- `searchArticles(query)` — filters by title/body containing query\n286\t- `getBookmarkedArticles()` — returns articles where `isBookmarked == true`\n287\t- `getRecentArticles()` — returns recently viewed (by date, limit 5-10)\n288\t\n289\t---\n290\t\n291\t## 9. Motion\n292\t\n293\t### Entry Animations\n294\t\n295\t- Screen push: 300ms slide + fade (standard page transition)\n296\t- Featured article card: 200ms fade-in on load\n297\t- Topic grid: Staggered reveal — each card fades in 50ms apart\n298\t- Recent articles: Horizontal slide-in from right, 300ms\n299\t\n300\t### Hero Transitions\n301\t\n302\t- When navigating from article card to Article Reader: 350ms fast-out-slow-in shared element transition on card image and title\n303\t\n304\t### Bottom Sheet Animations\n305\t\n306\t- Search overlay: 250ms smooth deceleration slide-up\n307\t- Sheet dismiss: 200ms slide-down with fade\n308\t\n309\t### Interactive Feedback\n310\t\n311\t- Card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%, then 200ms ease-out return\n312\t- Topic card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%\n313\t- Bookmark icon tap: 150ms scale bounce + color transition\n314\t- Search input focus: 200ms border color transition to `lavenderBloom`\n315\t\n316\t### Staggered List Reveals\n317\t\n318\t- When content loads: list items cascade into view — 50ms delay between each item\n319\t- Applies to topic grid (items appear 50ms apart)\n320\t\n321\t---\n322\t\n323\t## 10. Accessibility\n324\t\n325\t### Semantic Labels\n326\t\n327\t| Element | Semantic Label |\n328\t|---|---|\n329\t| AppBar | `'Education, back button to return to Library, search button'` |\n330\t| Search button | `'Search articles, double tap to search'` |\n331\t| Featured article | `'$articleTitle, featured article, $readTime to read, double tap to open'` |\n332\t| Topic card | `'$topicName, double tap to view $topicName articles'` |\n333\t| Recent article | `'$articleTitle, $topicName, $readTime, double tap to read'` |\n334\t| Bookmark icon | `'Bookmark article, ${isBookmarked ? 'bookmarked' : 'not bookmarked'}'` |\n335\t| Read time | `'$readTime to read'` |\n336\t\n337\t### Focus Order\n338\t\n339\t1. AppBar (back button → search button)\n340\t2. Featured article card\n341\t3. Topic cards (in grid order: Nutrition, Body Changes, Maternal Care, Exercise, Mental Health)\n342\t4. Recent article horizontal list (left to right)\n343\t5. Within each recent article: bookmark icon\n344\t\n345\t### Contrast Notes\n346\t\n347\t- `lavenderBloom` on `morningMist`: ~5.2:1 (passes AA)\n348\t- `deepGraphite` on `morningMist`: ~12:1 (passes AAA)\n349\t- `stoneGrey` on `morningMist`: ~4.7:1 (passes AA for body text)\n350\t- Dark mode: `twilightBloom` on `deepTwilight`: ~5.8:1 (passes AA)\n351\t\n352\t### Screen Reader Support\n353\t\n354\t- Announce article opened: \"Opening article: $title\"\n355\t- Announce bookmark toggled: \"Article ${isBookmarked ? 'bookmarked' : 'bookmark removed'}\"\n356\t- Announce search results: \"Found $count articles matching '$query'\"\n357\t- Use `Semantics` to label topic cards with topic name and article count if available\n358\t\n359\t### Touch Target Compliance\n360\t\n361\t- All interactive elements: 48dp minimum\n362\t- Topic cards: Full card area, minimum 48dp height\n363\t- Recent article cards: Full card area, 160dp width\n364\t- Bookmark icons: 48dp minimum touch target area (extends tappable area beyond icon itself)\n365\t- All buttons in AppBar: 48dp minimum height\n366\t\n367\t---\n368\t\n369\t## 11. Anti-Patterns\n370\t\n371\t**Do Not:**\n372\t- Add `BottomNavigationBar` (hidden per UX spec)\n373\t- Add FAB (Education screen has no primary action requiring FAB)\n374\t- Use `GridView` for recent articles (use horizontal `ListView` for horizontal scrolling)\n375\t- Add gradients to card backgrounds (flat `morningMist` only)\n376\t- Use platform default colors (all colors from design system)\n377\t- Use Inter, Roboto, or any font other than Nunito\n378\t- Create touch targets smaller than 48dp\n379\t- Use pure black (#000000) or pure white (#FFFFFF) for text\n380\t- Show featured article with hard-coded content in production (use provider data)\n381\t- Use `Navigator.push` instead of `context.push` with GoRouter\n382\t- Skip safe area handling\n383\t- Display empty state without illustration/guidance text\n384\t- Add shadows to AppBar (transparent/floating style per design system)\n385\t- Use default `Material` tap ripple — use scale feedback per design system\n386\t- Show all articles in recent if none are bookmarked — show \"no recent articles\" state\n387\t\n388\t---\n389\t\n390\t## 12. Critical Files for Implementation\n391\t\n392\t1. **`lib/screens/education/education_screen.dart`** — New file to create (main scaffold with CustomScrollView, AppBar with search, sections for Featured Article, Topics Grid, Recent Articles)\n393\t\n394\t2. **`lib/router/app_router.dart`** — Add GoRoute entry for `/education` pointing to `EducationScreen` and `/education/:topic` for topic-filtered article list\n395\t\n396\t3. **`lib/theme/app_theme.dart`** — Reference for design tokens (`AppTheme.spaceMd`, `AppTheme.radiusLg`, `AppTheme.lavenderBloom`, etc.) and typography via `Theme.of(context).textTheme`\n397\t\n398\t4. **`lib/screens/health_log/health_log_screen.dart`** — Reference implementation for a push-screen with `Scaffold`, `AppBar`, `ListView`/`CustomScrollView` body, card-based content with proper spacing and scale feedback patterns\n399\t\n400\t5. **`.stitch/UX.md` (Section 3.8)** — Reference for Education screen specification: scaffold structure (AppBar with search, hidden BottomNav, no FAB), sections (featured article, topics grid, recent articles), data requirements (`ArticleProvider`), and interaction patterns\n401\t\n402\t---\n403\t\n404\t## 13. Screen Structure\n405\t\n406\t```\n407\tEducationScreen\n408\t├── Scaffold\n409\t│   ├── AppBar (\"Education\", back button, search icon)\n410\t│   └── body: CustomScrollView\n411\t│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n412\t│       │   └── FeaturedArticleCard\n413\t│       │       ├── Hero image\n414\t│       │       ├── Topic badge\n415\t│       │       └── Content (title, read time)\n416\t│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n417\t│       │   └── SectionHeader(\"Topics\")\n418\t│       ├── SliverGrid (2 columns)\n419\t│       │   └── TopicCard × 5 (Nutrition, Body Changes, Maternal Care, Exercise, Mental Health)\n420\t│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n421\t│       │   └── SectionHeader(\"Recent Articles\")\n422\t│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n423\t│       │   └── RecentArticlesList (horizontal ListView)\n424\t│       │       └── ArticleCard × N\n425\t│       └── SliverToBoxAdapter (bottom padding)\n426\t├── Search icon → SearchOverlay\n427\t└── Topic card tap → /education/:topic\n428\t```"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f7a94ff0-43d7-45a8-89c7-107b23773d5e","uuid":"cfc2a67e-edd7-4b34-bb3a-1c99cfe7c117","timestamp":"2026-05-19T01:39:12.513Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.stitch/designs/education/SPEC.md","content":"# Education — Screen Specification\n\n## 1. Screen Title\n\n**Education**\n\n---\n\n## 2. Purpose\n\nBrowse and read trusted educational articles organized by topic. This screen serves as a content discovery hub, allowing users to explore curated health information relevant to their pregnancy journey. Users can filter by topic, search articles, and bookmark content for later reference.\n\n**Context:** Push route from Library tab. BottomNavigationBar is hidden. Primary actions are topic filtering, search, and article navigation.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Route\n\n`/education`\n\n---\n\n## 4. Widget Name\n\n`EducationScreen`\n\n---\n\n## 5. Design Tokens\n\n### Colors (Light Theme — from DESIGN.md Section 2)\n\n| Token | Hex | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary brand, AppBar, topic icons (Nutrition, Maternal Care) |\n| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n| `blushRose` | `#F9A8D4` | Secondary accent, Mental Health topic icon |\n| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Tertiary, success states, bookmark active indicator |\n| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text |\n| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, captions, timestamps |\n| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | Borders, dividers |\n| `softCoral` | `#EF4444` | Error states |\n| `warmWhite` | `#FFFFFF` | Bottom nav background, sheets |\n\n### Colors (Dark Theme)\n\n| Token | Hex | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `twilightBloom` | `#9F67FF` | Primary brand in dark mode |\n| `duskyRose` | `#FBC4E0` | Secondary accent in dark mode |\n| `nightMint` | `#34D399` | Tertiary success in dark mode |\n| `deepTwilight` | `#1E1B2E` | Card backgrounds in dark mode |\n| `nightSky` | `#13111C` | Scaffold background in dark mode |\n| `softPearl` | `#F3F4F6` | Primary text in dark mode |\n| `mutedSilver` | `#9CA3AF` | Secondary text in dark mode |\n| `deepBorder` | `#2D2B3A` | Borders in dark mode |\n\n### Typography (Nunito — Google Fonts from DESIGN.md Section 3)\n\n| Style | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| `displayLarge` | 32sp | 700 | 40sp | Hero article title on featured card |\n| `headlineMedium` | 22sp | 600 | 28sp | Section headers |\n| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | 28sp | AppBar title |\n| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | 24sp | Article card titles, topic card titles |\n| `bodyLarge` | 16sp | 400 | 24sp | Primary body text, article descriptions |\n| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | Secondary text, descriptions, card subtitles |\n| `labelLarge` | 14sp | 600 | 20sp | Button text, chip labels |\n| `caption` | 11sp | 500 | 16sp | Badges, timestamps, read time |\n\n### Spacing (8pt base from DESIGN.md Section 5 / UX.md Section 6)\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `xxs` | 4dp |\n| `xs` | 8dp |\n| `sm` | 12dp |\n| `md` | 16dp |\n| `lg` | 24dp |\n| `xl` | 32dp |\n| `xxl` | 48dp |\n\n### Corner Radius\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `sm` | 8dp (chips) |\n| `md` | 12dp |\n| `lg` | 16dp (standard cards, featured article card) |\n| `full` | 999dp (FAB, pills) |\n\n### Motion (from DESIGN.md Section 6 / UX.md Section 6)\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `durationShort` | 200ms |\n| `durationMedium` | 300ms |\n| `durationLong` | 350ms |\n| `staggerDelay` | 50ms between items |\n| `easingStandard` | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n| `easingEnter` | `Curves.easeOut` |\n| `easingExit` | `Curves.easeIn` |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Layout Rules\n\n### Scaffold Structure\n\n- `Scaffold` with `CustomScrollView` body (requires `SliverAppBar` for scroll behavior)\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Education\", back button, trailing search icon button\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden (per UX.md 3.8)\n- `FAB`: None\n\n### AppBar Behavior\n\n- Background: `lavenderTint` (#F5F3FF) / Night Sky (#13111C) in dark mode\n- Title: \"Education\" (SemiBold 20sp, `deepGraphite` / `softPearl` in dark mode)\n- Leading: Back button with 48dp touch target\n- Trailing: Search icon button (48dp touch target) to open search overlay\n\n### Body Layout\n\n- `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar` (collapsing header not needed — content scrolls beneath)\n- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for Featured Article at top\n- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for section header \"Topics\"\n- `SliverGrid` for Topics (2 columns)\n- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for section header \"Recent Articles\"\n- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for Recent Articles (horizontal `ListView`)\n- Bottom padding: 24dp for safe area\n\n---\n\n## 7. Sections\n\n### Section 1: Featured Article\n\n**Description:** Hero card at the top showcasing the current featured article with large image and headline.\n\n**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `Card`\n\n**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, stacked vertically (image top, content bottom).\n\n**Components:**\n- Article hero image: Full-width, 180dp height, `radiusLg` top corners, placeholder gradient if no image\n- Topic badge: Pill chip at top-left of image, `lavenderBloom` background\n- Title: \"Featured Article\" prefix label (`caption`, `stoneGrey`) + Article title (`displayLarge` 32sp, `deepGraphite`)\n- Read time: Clock icon + \"X min read\" (`caption`, `stoneGrey`)\n- Tap entire card → `/article-reader/:id`\n\n**Card Specifications:**\n- Background: `morningMist` (#FAFAFA) / `deepTwilight` in dark mode\n- Corner radius: `radiusLg` (16dp)\n- Shadow: Soft diffused — 8dp blur, 2dp offset-y, rgba(0,0,0,0.08) light / rgba(0,0,0,0.25) dark\n- Internal padding: 16dp all sides\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- Static featured article from article catalog (for MVP)\n- Fields: `id`, `title`, `topic`, `illustrationUrl`, `readTime`\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap card → push `/article-reader/:id`\n\n**Tap Feedback:** 200ms scale to 98% with 200ms return\n\n---\n\n### Section 2: Topics Grid\n\n**Description:** 2-column grid of topic category cards for filtering articles.\n\n**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `GridView` with `shrinkWrap: true` and `physics: NeverScrollableScrollPhysics()` OR separate `SliverGrid`\n\n**Layout:** 2 columns, 12dp gap between items, 16dp horizontal padding.\n\n**Topic Cards (5 total):**\n1. **Nutrition** — Icon: `Icons.restaurant_outlined`, color: `lavenderBloom`\n2. **Body Changes** — Icon: `Icons.pregnant_woman_outlined`, color: `blushRose`\n3. **Maternal Care** — Icon: `Icons.medical_services_outlined`, color: `lavenderBloom`\n4. **Exercise** — Icon: `Icons.fitness_center_outlined`, color: `softMint`\n5. **Mental Health** — Icon: `Icons.psychology_outlined`, color: `blushRose`\n\n**Each Topic Card:**\n- Size: Square-ish, aspect ratio ~1.3:1 (height slightly greater than width)\n- Background: `morningMist` / `deepTwilight` in dark mode\n- 48dp circular icon container at top with topic color at 15% opacity fill\n- Icon: 24sp, topic color\n- Title: Topic name (`titleMedium`, centered)\n- Corner radius: `radiusLg` (16dp)\n- Tap feedback: 200ms scale to 98%\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap topic card → `/education/:topic` (filtered article list)\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- Static topic list (for MVP)\n- `ArticleTopic` enum: `nutrition`, `bodyChanges`, `maternalCare`, `exercise`, `mentalHealth`\n\n---\n\n### Section 3: Recent Articles\n\n**Description:** Horizontal scrollable list of recently viewed articles for quick re-access.\n\n**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `SizedBox` with horizontal `ListView`\n\n**Layout:** Horizontal scrolling `ListView` with `SizedBox` height ~220dp, 16dp horizontal padding.\n\n**Each Article Card:**\n- Width: 160dp fixed\n- Background: `morningMist` / `deepTwilight`\n- Corner radius: `radiusLg` (16dp)\n- Vertical stack:\n  - Placeholder image area: 80dp height, `radiusSm` top corners, `lavenderTint` fill with centered icon\n  - Title: `titleMedium`, max 2 lines, ellipsis overflow\n  - Topic badge: Small pill below title\n  - Read time: `caption` below topic badge\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap article card → `/article-reader/:id`\n- Tap bookmark icon on card → toggle bookmark state\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- `ArticleProvider.articles` filtered for `isBookmarked == true` OR recently viewed (date-based)\n\n---\n\n### Section 4: Search Overlay\n\n**Description:** Full-screen overlay for searching articles by keyword.\n\n**Trigger:** Tap search icon in AppBar\n\n**Widget Type:** `showModalBottomSheet` with `Column` OR separate overlay route\n\n**Layout:** Bottom sheet or full-screen overlay with search input at top and results below.\n\n**Components:**\n- Search input field: `TextField` with search icon prefix, clear button suffix\n- Recent searches: List of recent search terms (tappable chips)\n- Search results: Vertical list of `Article` cards matching query\n- Empty state: \"No articles found\" with search icon\n\n**Data Operations:**\n- On search submit: Filter `ArticleProvider.articles` by title/body containing query string\n\n---\n\n## 8. Data\n\n### Entity: Article\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `id` | `String` (UUID) | Yes | Unique identifier |\n| `title` | `String` | Yes | Article title |\n| `topic` | `ArticleTopic` | Yes | Topic category for filtering |\n| `body` | `String` | Yes | Rich text article content |\n| `illustrationUrl` | `String` | No | Hero image URL |\n| `readTime` | `String` | No | Estimated read time (e.g., \"5 min\") |\n| `isBookmarked` | `bool` | Yes | Whether user has bookmarked this article |\n| `relatedArticleIds` | `List<String>` | Yes | IDs of related articles shown at bottom |\n\n### Enum: ArticleTopic\n\n| Value | Display Name | Icon |\n|---|---|---|\n| `nutrition` | Nutrition | `Icons.restaurant_outlined` |\n| `bodyChanges` | Body Changes | `Icons.pregnant_woman_outlined` |\n| `maternalCare` | Maternal Care | `Icons.medical_services_outlined` |\n| `exercise` | Exercise | `Icons.fitness_center_outlined` |\n| `mentalHealth` | Mental Health | `Icons.psychology_outlined` |\n\n### Provider: ArticleProvider\n\n**State:**\n- `articles: List<Article>` — all articles (static catalog for MVP)\n- `bookmarkedIds: Set<String>` — IDs of bookmarked articles\n- `recentSearches: List<String>` — recent search terms\n\n**Methods:**\n- `getArticlesByTopic(topic)` — filters articles by `ArticleTopic`\n- `toggleBookmark(id)` — toggles `isBookmarked` state\n- `searchArticles(query)` — filters by title/body containing query\n- `getBookmarkedArticles()` — returns articles where `isBookmarked == true`\n- `getRecentArticles()` — returns recently viewed (by date, limit 5-10)\n\n---\n\n## 9. Motion\n\n### Entry Animations\n\n- Screen push: 300ms slide + fade (standard page transition)\n- Featured article card: 200ms fade-in on load\n- Topic grid: Staggered reveal — each card fades in 50ms apart\n- Recent articles: Horizontal slide-in from right, 300ms\n\n### Hero Transitions\n\n- When navigating from article card to Article Reader: 350ms fast-out-slow-in shared element transition on card image and title\n\n### Bottom Sheet Animations\n\n- Search overlay: 250ms smooth deceleration slide-up\n- Sheet dismiss: 200ms slide-down with fade\n\n### Interactive Feedback\n\n- Card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%, then 200ms ease-out return\n- Topic card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%\n- Bookmark icon tap: 150ms scale bounce + color transition\n- Search input focus: 200ms border color transition to `lavenderBloom`\n\n### Staggered List Reveals\n\n- When content loads: list items cascade into view — 50ms delay between each item\n- Applies to topic grid (items appear 50ms apart)\n\n---\n\n## 10. Accessibility\n\n### Semantic Labels\n\n| Element | Semantic Label |\n|---|---|\n| AppBar | `'Education, back button to return to Library, search button'` |\n| Search button | `'Search articles, double tap to search'` |\n| Featured article | `'$articleTitle, featured article, $readTime to read, double tap to open'` |\n| Topic card | `'$topicName, double tap to view $topicName articles'` |\n| Recent article | `'$articleTitle, $topicName, $readTime, double tap to read'` |\n| Bookmark icon | `'Bookmark article, ${isBookmarked ? 'bookmarked' : 'not bookmarked'}'` |\n| Read time | `'$readTime to read'` |\n\n### Focus Order\n\n1. AppBar (back button → search button)\n2. Featured article card\n3. Topic cards (in grid order: Nutrition, Body Changes, Maternal Care, Exercise, Mental Health)\n4. Recent article horizontal list (left to right)\n5. Within each recent article: bookmark icon\n\n### Contrast Notes\n\n- `lavenderBloom` on `morningMist`: ~5.2:1 (passes AA)\n- `deepGraphite` on `morningMist`: ~12:1 (passes AAA)\n- `stoneGrey` on `morningMist`: ~4.7:1 (passes AA for body text)\n- Dark mode: `twilightBloom` on `deepTwilight`: ~5.8:1 (passes AA)\n\n### Screen Reader Support\n\n- Announce article opened: \"Opening article: $title\"\n- Announce bookmark toggled: \"Article ${isBookmarked ? 'bookmarked' : 'bookmark removed'}\"\n- Announce search results: \"Found $count articles matching '$query'\"\n- Use `Semantics` to label topic cards with topic name and article count if available\n\n### Touch Target Compliance\n\n- All interactive elements: 48dp minimum\n- Topic cards: Full card area, minimum 48dp height\n- Recent article cards: Full card area, 160dp width\n- Bookmark icons: 48dp minimum touch target area (extends tappable area beyond icon itself)\n- All buttons in AppBar: 48dp minimum height\n\n---\n\n## 11. Anti-Patterns\n\n**Do Not:**\n- Add `BottomNavigationBar` (hidden per UX spec)\n- Add FAB (Education screen has no primary action requiring FAB)\n- Use `GridView` for recent articles (use horizontal `ListView` for horizontal scrolling)\n- Add gradients to card backgrounds (flat `morningMist` only)\n- Use platform default colors (all colors from design system)\n- Use Inter, Roboto, or any font other than Nunito\n- Create touch targets smaller than 48dp\n- Use pure black (#000000) or pure white (#FFFFFF) for text\n- Show featured article with hard-coded content in production (use provider data)\n- Use `Navigator.push` instead of `context.push` with GoRouter\n- Skip safe area handling\n- Display empty state without illustration/guidance text\n- Add shadows to AppBar (transparent/floating style per design system)\n- Use default `Material` tap ripple — use scale feedback per design system\n- Show all articles in recent if none are bookmarked — show \"no recent articles\" state\n\n---\n\n## 12. Critical Files for Implementation\n\n1. **`lib/screens/education/education_screen.dart`** — New file to create (main scaffold with CustomScrollView, AppBar with search, sections for Featured Article, Topics Grid, Recent Articles)\n\n2. **`lib/router/app_router.dart`** — Add GoRoute entry for `/education` pointing to `EducationScreen` and `/education/:topic` for topic-filtered article list\n\n3. **`lib/theme/app_theme.dart`** — Reference for design tokens (`AppTheme.spaceMd`, `AppTheme.radiusLg`, `AppTheme.lavenderBloom`, etc.) and typography via `Theme.of(context).textTheme`\n\n4. **`lib/screens/health_log/health_log_screen.dart`** — Reference implementation for a push-screen with `Scaffold`, `AppBar`, `ListView`/`CustomScrollView` body, card-based content with proper spacing and scale feedback patterns\n\n5. **`.stitch/UX.md` (Section 3.8)** — Reference for Education screen specification: scaffold structure (AppBar with search, hidden BottomNav, no FAB), sections (featured article, topics grid, recent articles), data requirements (`ArticleProvider`), and interaction patterns\n\n---\n\n## 13. Screen Structure\n\n```\nEducationScreen\n├── Scaffold\n│   ├── AppBar (\"Education\", back button, search icon)\n│   └── body: CustomScrollView\n│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n│       │   └── FeaturedArticleCard\n│       │       ├── Hero image\n│       │       ├── Topic badge\n│       │       └── Content (title, read time)\n│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n│       │   └── SectionHeader(\"Topics\")\n│       ├── SliverGrid (2 columns)\n│       │   └── TopicCard × 5 (Nutrition, Body Changes, Maternal Care, Exercise, Mental Health)\n│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n│       │   └── SectionHeader(\"Recent Articles\")\n│       ├── SliverToBoxAdapter\n│       │   └── RecentArticlesList (horizontal ListView)\n│       │       └── ArticleCard × N\n│       └── SliverToBoxAdapter (bottom padding)\n├── Search icon → SearchOverlay\n└── Topic card tap → /education/:topic\n```","numLines":428,"startLine":1,"totalLines":428}}}
