106	
107	## 6. Layout Rules
108	
109	### Scaffold Structure
110	
111	- `Scaffold` with `CustomScrollView` body (requires `SliverAppBar` for scroll behavior)
112	- `AppBar`: Title "Education", back button, trailing search icon button
113	- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden (per UX.md 3.8)
114	- `FAB`: None
115	
116	### AppBar Behavior
117	
118	- Background: `lavenderTint` (#F5F3FF) / Night Sky (#13111C) in dark mode
119	- Title: "Education" (SemiBold 20sp, `deepGraphite` / `softPearl` in dark mode)
120	- Leading: Back button with 48dp touch target
121	- Trailing: Search icon button (48dp touch target) to open search overlay
122	
123	### Body Layout
124	
125	- `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar` (collapsing header not needed — content scrolls beneath)
126	- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for Featured Article at top
127	- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for section header "Topics"
128	- `SliverGrid` for Topics (2 columns)
129	- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for section header "Recent Articles"
130	- `SliverToBoxAdapter` for Recent Articles (horizontal `ListView`)
131	- Bottom padding: 24dp for safe area
132	
133	---
134	
135	## 7. Sections
136	
137	### Section 1: Featured Article
138	
139	**Description:** Hero card at the top showcasing the current featured article with large image and headline.
140	
141	**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `Card`
142	
143	**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, stacked vertically (image top, content bottom).
144	
145	**Components:**
146	- Article hero image: Full-width, 180dp height, `radiusLg` top corners, placeholder gradient if no image
147	- Topic badge: Pill chip at top-left of image, `lavenderBloom` background
148	- Title: "Featured Article" prefix label (`caption`, `stoneGrey`) + Article title (`displayLarge` 32sp, `deepGraphite`)
149	- Read time: Clock icon + "X min read" (`caption`, `stoneGrey`)
150	- Tap entire card → `/article-reader/:id`
151	
152	**Card Specifications:**
153	- Background: `morningMist` (#FAFAFA) / `deepTwilight` in dark mode
154	- Corner radius: `radiusLg` (16dp)
155	- Shadow: Soft diffused — 8dp blur, 2dp offset-y, rgba(0,0,0,0.08) light / rgba(0,0,0,0.25) dark
156	- Internal padding: 16dp all sides
157	
158	**Data Requirements:**
159	- Static featured article from article catalog (for MVP)
160	- Fields: `id`, `title`, `topic`, `illustrationUrl`, `readTime`
161	
162	**Interactive Elements:**
163	- Tap card → push `/article-reader/:id`
164	
165	**Tap Feedback:** 200ms scale to 98% with 200ms return
166	
167	---
168	
169	### Section 2: Topics Grid
170	
171	**Description:** 2-column grid of topic category cards for filtering articles.
172	
173	**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `GridView` with `shrinkWrap: true` and `physics: NeverScrollableScrollPhysics()` OR separate `SliverGrid`
174	
175	**Layout:** 2 columns, 12dp gap between items, 16dp horizontal padding.
176	
177	**Topic Cards (5 total):**
178	1. **Nutrition** — Icon: `Icons.restaurant_outlined`, color: `lavenderBloom`
179	2. **Body Changes** — Icon: `Icons.pregnant_woman_outlined`, color: `blushRose`
180	3. **Maternal Care** — Icon: `Icons.medical_services_outlined`, color: `lavenderBloom`
181	4. **Exercise** — Icon: `Icons.fitness_center_outlined`, color: `softMint`
182	5. **Mental Health** — Icon: `Icons.psychology_outlined`, color: `blushRose`
183	
184	**Each Topic Card:**
185	- Size: Square-ish, aspect ratio ~1.3:1 (height slightly greater than width)
186	- Background: `morningMist` / `deepTwilight` in dark mode
187	- 48dp circular icon container at top with topic color at 15% opacity fill
188	- Icon: 24sp, topic color
189	- Title: Topic name (`titleMedium`, centered)
190	- Corner radius: `radiusLg` (16dp)
191	- Tap feedback: 200ms scale to 98%
192	
193	**Interactive Elements:**
194	- Tap topic card → `/education/:topic` (filtered article list)
195	
196	**Data Requirements:**
197	- Static topic list (for MVP)
198	- `ArticleTopic` enum: `nutrition`, `bodyChanges`, `maternalCare`, `exercise`, `mentalHealth`
199	
200	---
201	
202	### Section 3: Recent Articles
203	
204	**Description:** Horizontal scrollable list of recently viewed articles for quick re-access.
205	
206	**Widget Type:** `SliverToBoxAdapter` containing a `SizedBox` with horizontal `ListView`
207	
208	**Layout:** Horizontal scrolling `ListView` with `SizedBox` height ~220dp, 16dp horizontal padding.
209	
210	**Each Article Card:**
211	- Width: 160dp fixed
212	- Background: `morningMist` / `deepTwilight`
213	- Corner radius: `radiusLg` (16dp)
214	- Vertical stack:
215	  - Placeholder image area: 80dp height, `radiusSm` top corners, `lavenderTint` fill with centered icon
216	  - Title: `titleMedium`, max 2 lines, ellipsis overflow
217	  - Topic badge: Small pill below title
218	  - Read time: `caption` below topic badge
219	
220	**Interactive Elements:**
221	- Tap article card → `/article-reader/:id`
222	- Tap bookmark icon on card → toggle bookmark state
223	
224	**Data Requirements:**
225	- `ArticleProvider.articles` filtered for `isBookmarked == true` OR recently viewed (date-based)
226	
227	---
228	
229	### Section 4: Search Overlay
230	
231	**Description:** Full-screen overlay for searching articles by keyword.
232	
233	**Trigger:** Tap search icon in AppBar
234	
235	**Widget Type:** `showModalBottomSheet` with `Column` OR separate overlay route
236	
237	**Layout:** Bottom sheet or full-screen overlay with search input at top and results below.
238	
239	**Components:**
240	- Search input field: `TextField` with search icon prefix, clear button suffix
241	- Recent searches: List of recent search terms (tappable chips)
242	- Search results: Vertical list of `Article` cards matching query
243	- Empty state: "No articles found" with search icon
244	
245	**Data Operations:**
246	- On search submit: Filter `ArticleProvider.articles` by title/body containing query string
247	
248	---
249	
250	## 8. Data
251	
252	### Entity: Article
253	
254	| Field | Type | Required | Description |
255	|---|---|---|---|
256	| `id` | `String` (UUID) | Yes | Unique identifier |
257	| `title` | `String` | Yes | Article title |
258	| `topic` | `ArticleTopic` | Yes | Topic category for filtering |
259	| `body` | `String` | Yes | Rich text article content |
260	| `illustrationUrl` | `String` | No | Hero image URL |
261	| `readTime` | `String` | No | Estimated read time (e.g., "5 min") |
262	| `isBookmarked` | `bool` | Yes | Whether user has bookmarked this article |
263	| `relatedArticleIds` | `List<String>` | Yes | IDs of related articles shown at bottom |
264	
265	### Enum: ArticleTopic
266	
267	| Value | Display Name | Icon |
268	|---|---|---|
269	| `nutrition` | Nutrition | `Icons.restaurant_outlined` |
270	| `bodyChanges` | Body Changes | `Icons.pregnant_woman_outlined` |
271	| `maternalCare` | Maternal Care | `Icons.medical_services_outlined` |
272	| `exercise` | Exercise | `Icons.fitness_center_outlined` |
273	| `mentalHealth` | Mental Health | `Icons.psychology_outlined` |
274	
275	### Provider: ArticleProvider
276	
277	**State:**
278	- `articles: List<Article>` — all articles (static catalog for MVP)
279	- `bookmarkedIds: Set<String>` — IDs of bookmarked articles
280	- `recentSearches: List<String>` — recent search terms
281	
282	**Methods:**
283	- `getArticlesByTopic(topic)` — filters articles by `ArticleTopic`
284	- `toggleBookmark(id)` — toggles `isBookmarked` state
285	- `searchArticles(query)` — filters by title/body containing query
286	- `getBookmarkedArticles()` — returns articles where `isBookmarked == true`
287	- `getRecentArticles()` — returns recently viewed (by date, limit 5-10)
288	
289	---
290	
291	## 9. Motion
292	
293	### Entry Animations
294	
295	- Screen push: 300ms slide + fade (standard page transition)
296	- Featured article card: 200ms fade-in on load
297	- Topic grid: Staggered reveal — each card fades in 50ms apart
298	- Recent articles: Horizontal slide-in from right, 300ms
299	
300	### Hero Transitions
301	
302	- When navigating from article card to Article Reader: 350ms fast-out-slow-in shared element transition on card image and title
303	
304	### Bottom Sheet Animations
305	
306	- Search overlay: 250ms smooth deceleration slide-up
307	- Sheet dismiss: 200ms slide-down with fade
308	
309	### Interactive Feedback
310	
311	- Card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%, then 200ms ease-out return
312	- Topic card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98%
313	- Bookmark icon tap: 150ms scale bounce + color transition
314	- Search input focus: 200ms border color transition to `lavenderBloom`
315	
316	### Staggered List Reveals
317	
318	- When content loads: list items cascade into view — 50ms delay between each item
319	- Applies to topic grid (items appear 50ms apart)
320	
321	---
322	
323	## 10. Accessibility
324	
325	### Semantic Labels
326	
327	| Element | Semantic Label |
328	|---|---|
329	| AppBar | `'Education, back button to return to Library, search button'` |
330	| Search button | `'Search articles, double tap to search'` |
331	| Featured article | `'$articleTitle, featured article, $readTime to read, double tap to open'` |
332	| Topic card | `'$topicName, double tap to view $topicName articles'` |
333	| Recent article | `'$articleTitle, $topicName, $readTime, double tap to read'` |
334	| Bookmark icon | `'Bookmark article, ${isBookmarked ? 'bookmarked' : 'not bookmarked'}'` |
335	| Read time | `'$readTime to read'` |
336	
337	### Focus Order
338	
339	1. AppBar (back button → search button)
340	2. Featured article card
341	3. Topic cards (in grid order: Nutrition, Body Changes, Maternal Care, Exercise, Mental Health)
342	4. Recent article horizontal list (left to right)
343	5. Within each recent article: bookmark icon
344	
345	### Contrast Notes
346	
347	- `lavenderBloom` on `morningMist`: ~5.2:1 (passes AA)
348	- `deepGraphite` on `morningMist`: ~12:1 (passes AAA)
349	- `stoneGrey` on `morningMist`: ~4.7:1 (passes AA for body text)
350	- Dark mode: `twilightBloom` on `deepTwilight`: ~5.8:1 (passes AA)
351	
352	### Screen Reader Support
353	
354	- Announce article opened: "Opening article: $title"
355	- Announce bookmark toggled: "Article ${isBookmarked ? 'bookmarked' : 'bookmark removed'}"
356	- Announce search results: "Found $count articles matching '$query'"
357	- Use `Semantics` to label topic cards with topic name and article count if available
358	
359	### Touch Target Compliance
360	
361	- All interactive elements: 48dp minimum
362	- Topic cards: Full card area, minimum 48dp height
363	- Recent article cards: Full card area, 160dp width
364	- Bookmark icons: 48dp minimum touch target area (extends tappable area beyond icon itself)
365	- All buttons in AppBar: 48dp minimum height
366	
367	---
368	
369	## 11. Anti-Patterns
370	
371	**Do Not:**
372	- Add `BottomNavigationBar` (hidden per UX spec)
373	- Add FAB (Education screen has no primary action requiring FAB)
374	- Use `GridView` for recent articles (use horizontal `ListView` for horizontal scrolling)
375	- Add gradients to card backgrounds (flat `morningMist` only)
376	- Use platform default colors (all colors from design system)
377	- Use Inter, Roboto, or any font other than Nunito
378	- Create touch targets smaller than 48dp
379	- Use pure black (#000000) or pure white (#FFFFFF) for text
380	- Show featured article with hard-coded content in production (use provider data)
381	- Use `Navigator.push` instead of `context.push` with GoRouter
382	- Skip safe area handling
383	- Display empty state without illustration/guidance text
384	- Add shadows to AppBar (transparent/floating style per design system)
385	- Use default `Material` tap ripple — use scale feedback per design system
386	- Show all articles in recent if none are bookmarked — show "no recent articles" state
387	
388	---
